services:
  jellyfin:
    image: dockerhub.imgki.com/nyanmisaka/jellyfin:latest
    container_name: jellyfin
    restart: unless-stopped
    ports:
      - "8097:8096" # Main web interface
      - "8920:8920" # Optional: HTTPS port
      - "7359:7359/udp" # Optional: Live TV and DVR
      - "1900:1900/udp" # Optional: DLNA
    volumes:
      - ./config:/config # Persistent storage for configuration
      - ./cache:/cache   # Cache directory
      - /root/smartstrm/data/strm:/media      
    environment:
      # Optional: Set PUID and PGID for file permissions if needed
       - PUID=1000
       - PGID=1000
      # Optional: Timezone setting
       - TZ=Asia/Shanghai
    devices:
      # Optional: For hardware acceleration (e.g., Intel Quick Sync, NVIDIA NVENC/NVDEC)
      # Uncomment and adjust based on your hardware and drivers
       - /dev/dri:/dev/dri # For Intel iGPU
      # - /dev/nvidia0:/dev/nvidia0 # For NVIDIA GPUs
      # - /dev/nvidiactl:/dev/nvidiactl
      # - /dev/nvidia-uvm:/dev/nvidia-uvm
      # - /dev/nvidia-modeset:/dev/nvidia-modeset
    # Optional: If you need host network for specific features like DLNA discovery
    # network_mode: host
